metadata.name: Cryptobilia #1
metadata.description: Cryptobilia is home to 5000 goats. They lived peacefully until the imposters arrived and wreaked havoc at the Battle Royale. The fans can no longer gather to watch the goats and superstars compete. The imposters have dropped off mysterious packages containing clues on their motives to invade Cryptobilia. These clues must be used to uncover the truth. Nobody knows why theyre here and where they came from...Or have they been here all along?
